OL,6,FThe Turkish football team president
OL,7,Fwho punched a referee, and has since
OL,8,Fresigned, has been handed a lifetime
OL,9,Fban by the country's football
OL,10,Ffederation.
OL,12,FFaruk Koca attacked referee Halil Umut
OL,13,FMeler on Monday, after a 1-1 draw
OL,14,Fbetween his team and Caykur Rizespor
OL,15,Fin Turkey's top league.
OL,17,FMeler, was left with a small fracture
OL,18,Fnear his eye following the incident.
